'''Frank Thelen''' is a businessman based in [[Bonn, Germany]]. He was a co-founder of companies such as ''Softer Solutions'' and ''doo''. As of 2014, he is the CEO of venture capital firm ''e42'',<ref>{{cite web|title=Frank Thelen on doo|url=http://www.celebritynetworth.com/video/frank-thelen-doo-517397013/|publisher=TechCrunch TV}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=doo launches Scanbot|url=http://tech.eu/features/988/doo-acquisition-interest-dropbox-scanbot/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Database e42|url=http://www.gruenderszene.de/datenbank/unternehmen/e42|publisher=Gründerszene}}</ref> which has invested in startups such as [[Wunderlist]].<ref>{{cite web|title=15 steps to launch your own startup in Europe – Part 5|url=http://christianreber.com/blog/15-steps-to-launch-your-own-startup-in-europe-part-5|publisher=Christian Reber, 6Wunderkinder|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219022441/http://christianreber.com/blog/15-steps-to-launch-your-own-startup-in-europe-part-5|archivedate=2013-12-19|df=}}</ref>
